        "title": "How to split the string with bullets(All types)using regex in java",
        "body": "<p>Below is my text<\/p>\n\n<pre><code> Welcome to java programming 1) Oops concepts a) Encapsulation A) Abstraction I) Inheritance  \u2022 Polymorphism\n2)sample program on java 1.Project source code \nsample text files \u2022 sample.txt b)sam.txt\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I want to split the text based on below pattern and remove the bullets<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>1)any bullet 1)I)a)A)\u2022\n2)followed by space\n3)followed by uppercase word\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>So i want to generate following result<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Welcome to java programming \nOops concepts \nEncapsulation \nAbstraction\nInheritance  \nPolymorphism\nsample program on java\nProject source code\nPlease suggest me how to do this\nsample text files\nsample.txt\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>sam.txt\nThanks<\/p>\n",
