            "creation_date": 1375945707,
            "body": "<p>This will work:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n    final String s = \"Welcome to java programming 1) Oops concepts a) Encapsulation A) Abstraction I) Inheritance  \u2022 Polymorphism\";\n    final String[] split = s.split(\"\\\\s*(\\\\w\\\\)|\u2022)\\\\s*\");\n    for (final String bullet : split) {\n        System.out.println(bullet);\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>The regex is<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>\\\\s*(\\\\w\\\\)|\u2022)\\\\s*\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>\\\\s*<\/code> - zero or more spaces<\/li>\n<li><code>(\\\\w\\\\)|\u2022)<\/code> - a digit or letter followed by a bracket or a bullet point<\/li>\n<li><code>\\\\s*<\/code> - zero or more spaces<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p>Output:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Welcome to java programming\nOops concepts\nEncapsulation\nAbstraction\nInheritance\nPolymorphism\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
