            "body": "<p>Following <em>positive lookahead<\/em> based regex should work for you:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String s = \"Welcome to java programming 1) Oops concepts a) Encapsulation A) Abstraction I) Inheritance  \u2022 Polymorphism\";\nString[] arr = s.split(\"\\\\s*([a-zA-Z\\\\d][).]|\u2022)\\\\s*(?=[A-Z])\");\nSystem.out.println(\"Split =&gt; \" + Arrays.toString(tok));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><strong>OUTPUT:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Split =&gt; [Welcome to java programming, Oops concepts, Encapsulation, Abstraction, Inheritance, Polymorphism]\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
