            "body": "<p>You can try this too <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String str=\"Welcome to java programming 1) Oops concepts a) Encapsulation A) Abstraction I) Inheritance  \u2022 Polymorphism\" ;\n    String newStr=str.replaceAll(\"(?i)\\\\s*([\\\\d\\\\w]\\\\)|\u2022)\\\\s*\",\" ISseperatorIS \");\n    String[] arr=newStr.split(\"ISseperatorIS \");\n    for(String i:arr){\n        System.out.println(i);\n    }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Out put<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Welcome to java programming \nOops concepts \nEncapsulation \nAbstraction \nInheritance \nPolymorphism\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
